<div id="review_1519780832" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1519780832" />
    <a title="Robyn" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/25037254-robyn"><img alt="Robyn" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1612026107p2/25037254.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1519780832?book_show_action=true">Jan 21, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Robyn" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Robyn" href="/user/show/25037254-robyn">Robyn</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/25037254-robyn?shelf=2016">2016</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1519780832" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7167529711878834553">I can&apos;t really put my finger on what it is that I&apos;m loving about this series. I can name the faults at length (but I won&apos;t) and I don&apos;t feel that I *should* like this as (gasp) I dislike both The Lord of the Rings and The Chronicles of Narnia, both of which seem to be major influences,, and yet! Totally enamoured. </span>
  <span id="freeText7167529711878834553" style="display:none">I can't really put my finger on what it is that I'm loving about this series. I can name the faults at length (but I won't) and I don't feel that I *should* like this as (gasp) I dislike both The Lord of the Rings and The Chronicles of Narnia, both of which seem to be major influences,, and yet! Totally enamoured. </span>
  <a data-text-id="7167529711878834553" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


