<li class='cover' id='bookCover_177250'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/177250.The_Mirror_of_Her_Dreams"><img alt="The Mirror of Her Dreams (Mordant&#39;s Need, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320541116l/177250._SX98_.jpg" />
